&lt;p class="western" align="JUSTIFY" style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"&gt;Escrito por&lt;span&gt; Rafaela Melo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Jul 2012 14:56:10 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/fisl13/noticias/saude-dos-trabalhadores-propriedade-intelectual-e-marco-civil-da-internet-em-debate-no-fisl13</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/fisl13/noticias/saude-dos-trabalhadores-propriedade-intelectual-e-marco-civil-da-internet-em-debate-no-fisl13</guid></item></channel></rss>